    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这场战争即将爆发；一场每个人都参与，但只有勇敢者主导的最后一场战争！“Bulletproof”不仅仅是一个名字，它是人类的故事！对我们来说，这是最后的机会！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/b89a689d9e9a730e5b51a275420cd573.poster.avif?t=1737224153\" width=800 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/b89a689d9e9a730e5b51a275420cd573.webm?t=1737224153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/b89a689d9e9a730e5b51a275420cd573.mp4?t=1737224153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >气候变化危机已经成为一个无法解决的问题。全球性问题如迁徙、干旱、人口增长、战争以及获取食物和水的困难，带来了巨大的挑战。为了解决这些问题，人类开发了一种先进的人工智能：EARTHCURE。然而，对于机器来说，事实仅仅是数字。EARTHCURE得出结论，为了让人类生存，全球99%的人口必须被消除。通过生物武器将人类转化为僵尸，EARTHCURE用新的战争机器和孵化中心将世界推向了大规模灭绝。一辆坦克和一名被军队遗弃的士兵……Bulletproof！虽然一切看似偶然，但实际上，这是人类的故事。这是你的故事！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/39893e4565445d8b60ba07aaf72bd450.poster.avif?t=1737224153\" width=800 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/39893e4565445d8b60ba07aaf72bd450.webm?t=1737224153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/39893e4565445d8b60ba07aaf72bd450.mp4?t=1737224153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bulletproof Tank Adventure是一款3D坦克战斗游戏，具有进度机制，专注于平台和各种地图，充满了压力和动作。Bulletproof将让你笑出声来，也会让你感到沮丧！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/a6a26a4c8120d80bed5787a1259d8538.poster.avif?t=1737224153\" width=800 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/a6a26a4c8120d80bed5787a1259d8538.webm?t=1737224153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337110/extras/a6a26a4c8120d80bed5787a1259d8538.mp4?t=1737224153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏机制</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据地形条件提供逼真的进展体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像飞越平台或地面一样的动作时刻。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满悬崖和爆炸的挑战性跌落。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有精确控制设置的生存斗争。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>武器</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种不同类型的炸弹。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机关枪。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特别适用于僵尸的近战武器。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地图</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战性的地形和轨道。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >泥泞区域，增加驾驶难度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火山、熔岩、间歇泉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沙漠环境、龙卷风、雾霾等。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>音乐</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为场景和关卡量身定制的音乐。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>内容</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要与时间赛跑的 платформы 和地图.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提示.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态游戏体验.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可定制设置.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可定制的图形选项.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低存储空间要求.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >七种不同的坦克类型.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三十种不同的颜色选项.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个坦克独特的属性.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敌人</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有不同种类和特征的坦克.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >僵尸.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备机枪的车辆.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配备智能导弹的车辆.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陷阱.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地雷，地雷雨.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EARTHCURE机器人等。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有你，这次冒险将不完整。与我们一起，你将决定这个故事的结局。分享你的想法和支持，会让我们感到在这次冒险中不再孤单。</p>",
